---
// App-shell header: serif maroon wordmark over a gold accent rule.
// Wordmark scales from the type scale (40px non-desktop → 62px desktop hero).
---

<header class="border-b border-rule-strong bg-gradient-to-b from-panel-from to-panel-to">
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-4 py-5 tablet:px-6 desktop:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
      <a href="/" class="no-underline">
        <span
          class="font-serif font-bold tracking-tight text-maroon text-[40px] leading-none desktop:text-[62px]"
        >
          obs-layouts
        </span>
      </a>
      <p class="font-sans text-[15px] text-ink-soft">
        Live broadcast slides for the
        <a
          href="https://www.youtube.com/@clockspinning"
          class="font-semibold"
          rel="noopener"
        >Clock Spinning Podcast</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4 h-px w-full bg-gold/60"></div>
  </div>
</header>
